body_html: Yep, I was just re-discovering this because of ongoing problems over in #1704 (but thank you for the pointer—it's good to confirm this is real behavior). These changes broke the workarounds that I was using to get around the broken protobuf behavior. I went your route, too: just blow everything away and pull new copies of everything. I'll update #1704 when the dust settles, since 14ac223 is supposed to fix this.

body: Yep, I was just re-discovering this because of ongoing problems over in #1704 (but thank you for the pointer—it's good to confirm this is real behavior). These changes broke the workarounds that I was using to get around the broken protobuf behavior. I went your route, too: just blow everything away and pull new copies of everything. I'll update #1704 when the dust settles, since [14ac223](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/commit/14ac2235699509f512b44b71160239c153ab413d) is supposed to fix this.
